    <area target="" alt="The Scry Tab<p>The Scrying function enables you to gain an extra boost of your choice in exchange for viewing a video advertisement which will help Divine Games gain some revenue.<p>The choices are: +100% production for 4 hours, +2 m/s and +10 mana regen for 10 minutes, Faction Coins based on your production. <p>Formula: ??? Events can bring additional options.<p>Some countries have more ads then others and players from those countries will be able to scry more often.<p> Some players will be able to scry as much as they want and have both timers running all the time, others may only be able to scry only once or twice per day and will need to be strategic about when to best use it.<p> A few people will not be able to scry at all." research="The Scry Tab<p>The Scrying function enables you to gain an extra boost of your choice in exchange for viewing a video advertisement which will help Divine Games gain some revenue.<p>The choices are: +100% production for 4 hours, +2 m/s and +10 mana regen for 10 minutes,<p> Faction Coins based on your production. <p>Formula :1 + floor(ln(1 + offline gold/s)^1.5).<p>Some countries have more ads then others and players from those countries will be able to scry more often.<p> Some players will be able to scry as much as they want and have both timers running all the time, others may only be able to scry only once or twice per day and will need to be strategic about when to best use it.<p> A few people will not be able to scry at all." coords="633,411,682,460" shape="rect">
