    <area target="" alt="Excavation / Artifacts<p> Excavation is unlocked once you have over 1B gems, produced over 10 Oc (1E28) coins and bought the Archeology Upgrade.<p>Excavating enables to find Rubies, Faction Coins and at certain thresholds or under certain conditions Artifacts. <p>Specific artifacts are required to unlock the Neutral &amp; Prestige Factions.<p>Excavation Reset  costs 1 Ruby up until 2999 excavations, switching to 2 Rubies at 3000 and above. It will reset the excavation counter to zero, all previously gained Excavation rewards and Rubies will persist and you can not find them again." research="Excavation / Artifacts<p> Excavation is unlocked once you have over 1B gems, produced over 10 Oc (1E28) coins and bought the Archeology Upgrade.<p>Excavating enables to find Rubies, Faction Coins and at certain thresholds or under certain conditions Artifacts. <p>Specific artifacts are required to unlock the Neutral &amp; Prestige Factions.<p>Excavation Reset  costs 1 Ruby up until 2999 excavations, switching to 2 Rubies at 3000 and above. It will reset the excavation counter to zero, all previously gained Excavation rewards and Rubies will persist and you can not find them again." coords="30,89,90,149" shape="rect">
    <area target="" alt="Research: R16+<p>Enter the Research Facilities to improve your grinding potential.<p>A new progress system accessible from R16, overtaking the Mercenaries and boosting the production of the 6 Vanilla Factions.<p>Later, at R23, it also includes the Neutral Factions." research="Research: R16+<p>Enter the Research Facilities to improve your grinding potential.<p>A new progress system accessible from R16, overtaking the Mercenaries and boosting the production of the 6 Vanilla Factions.<p>Later, at R23, it also includes the Neutral Factions." coords="33,163,90,219" shape="rect">
