    <area target="" alt="Priority Autocasting: Allows you to prioritize the order of spell casting. <p>Spells with lower priority will be cast only if the higher priority spells are already active. <p>Only while offline, increase your spells cast amount by 1 per minute.<p>Cost: 400 Ud (4E38)" research="Priority Autocasting: Allows you to prioritize the order of spell casting. <p>Spells with lower priority will be cast only if the higher priority spells are already active. <p>Only while offline, increase your spells cast amount by 1 per minute.<p>Cost: 400 Ud (4E38)" coords="678,305,8" shape="circle">
    <area target="" alt="Planned Autocasting: Allows you to set Primary and Secondary spells. Primary spells (Set with CTRL+Click) will fire when the mana reaches amount set by the Contingency slidebar. <p>Secondary spells (Set with SHIFT+Click) will fire as soon as there is enough mana, and if ALL the primary spells are active.<p>Only while offline, increase mana produced by an additional 10% of your mana regeneration per second and your spells cast amount by an additional 2 per minute.600 Spd (6E56)" research="Planned Autocasting: Allows you to set Primary and Secondary spells. Primary spells (Set with CTRL+Click) will fire when the mana reaches amount set by the Contingency slidebar. <p>Secondary spells (Set with SHIFT+Click) will fire as soon as there is enough mana, and if ALL the primary spells are active.<p>Only while offline, increase mana produced by an additional 10% of your mana regeneration per second and your spells cast amount by an additional 2 per minute.600 Spd (6E56)" coords="678,264,8" shape="circle">
    <area target="" alt="Efficient Autocasting: <p>Allows you to set spells to work outside of contingency and planned settings. These spells (set with CTRL+SHIFT+Click), or in the spell tooltip,disregard your contingency rules and are casted as soon as you have enough mana for them.<p>Cost: 700 Vg (7E65)<p>Only while offline, increase your mana production by an additional 10% of your mana regeneration per second, and your spells cast amount by an additional 2 per minute." research="Efficient Autocasting: <p>Allows you to set spells to work outside of contingency and planned settings. These spells (set with CTRL+SHIFT+Click), or in the spell tooltip,disregard your contingency rules and are casted as soon as you have enough mana for them.<p>Cost: 700 Vg (7E65)<p>Only while offline, increase your mana production by an additional 10% of your mana regeneration per second, and your spells cast amount by an additional 2 per minute." coords="678,220,7" shape="circle">
